Record Class DefaultErrorMessageFactory

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.embeds.error.DefaultErrorMessageFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
ErrorMessageFactory, Implementation.ExtensionProvidable
public record DefaultErrorMessageFactory(Embeds embeds) extends Record implements ErrorMessageFactory
The default implementation of ErrorMessageFactory. Supports loading the embeds from an EmbedDataSource.
See Also:
